name: Engauge Analytics
author: Doug Black

sections.description:
Engauge Analytics: Analytics without the Evil.

This plugin enables Engauge for your entire WordPress site. Lightweight and fast with plenty of great features.

Features

  • Blazing fast performance
  • Does one thing and does it well
  • Drop-dead simple and easy to use
  • Regularly updated and “future proof”
  • Stays current with the latest tracking code
  • Easy to customize the tracking code

Thank you to Jeff Starr for the assistance on this!

For more information, check out Engauge Analytics
sections.changelog:
1.6 – Added WP icons, tested with 5.3

1.3 – Fixes render blocking issue
